data.description: This is a 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom brick ranch. This home features hardwood floors and carpet. There is a fireplace in the den/family room, finished basement with fireplace into living area, 2 full baths one on main floor and one in basement. 2 car detached garage in fenced yard. This property will be sold " As Is". Buyer responsible for any municipal requirements and buyer to verify all information including square footage, taxes, features and measurements. Property under probate and subject to third party approval. 24 hour notice required for showings.
